Vanguard Fenway Funds - Vanguard Growth Equity Fund: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 28, 2017 11:14 PM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of Vanguard Fenway Funds - Vanguard Growth Equity Fund



Snapshot People




Company Overview
As of February 21, 2014 Vanguard Fenway Funds - Vanguard Growth Equity Fund has been acquired by Vanguard World Fund - Vanguard U.S. Growth Fund. Vanguard Fenway Funds - Vanguard Growth Equity Fund is an open-ended equity mutual fund launched by The Vanguard Group, Inc. It is co-managed by Jennison Associates LLC and Baillie Gifford Overseas Ltd. The fund invests in the public equity markets of the United States. It invests in stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. The fund invests in growth-oriented value stocks of mid-cap and large-cap companies. It employs a combination of fundamental and quantitative analysis with a bottom-up stock picking approach focusing on factors ...
As of February 21, 2014 Vanguard Fenway Funds - Vanguard Growth Equity Fund has been acquired by Vanguard World Fund - Vanguard U.S. Growth Fund. Vanguard Fenway Funds - Vanguard Growth Equity Fund is an open-ended equity mutual fund launched by The Vanguard Group, Inc. It is co-managed by Jennison Associates LLC and Baillie Gifford Overseas Ltd. The fund invests in the public equity markets of the United States. It invests in stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. The fund invests in growth-oriented value stocks of mid-cap and large-cap companies. It employs a combination of fundamental and quantitative analysis with a bottom-up stock picking approach focusing on factors like earnings growth, cash-flow generation, profitability, interest coverage, balance-sheet strength, financial prospects, the prices of the securities, and the stock market and economy in general to create its portfolio. The fund benchmarks the performance of its portfolio against the Russell 1000 Growth Index. It was formerly known as Turner Funds - Turner Growth Equity Fund. Vanguard Fenway Funds - Vanguard Growth Equity Fund was formed on March 11, 1992 and is domiciled in the United States.
Detailed Description


466 Lexington AvenueNew York, NY 10017United StatesFounded in 1992



Phone: 212-421-1000

Fax: 212-682-9831








